Packages 
Package Description
account
Provides the classes necessary to manage different types of accounts for a user.
atm
This package contains all classes which closely relate to or interact with the ATM machine.
bankmanager
Provides the classes necessary to handle user and atm requests that require high-level authorization.
broker
This package represents a stock broker who handles the buying and selling of stocks.
interfaces
This package represents the interfaces displayed to the person using the ATM.
investments
This package is used for all investment activities done for the user.
subscriptions
Package represents subscription services the user can subscribe to and will be charged at the beginning of the month.
